'''''Shangani Patrol''''' ni filime y'intambara ishingiye ku gitabo kitari ibihimbano ''A Time to Die'' cyanditswe na Robert Cary (1968), hamwe n’amateka ya Shangani Patrol, hamwe na Brian O'Shaughnessy nka Major Allan Wilson na Will Hutchins nk'umuskuti Frederick. Russell Burnham . <ref>Shangani Patrol soundtrack album cover, RPM 1053-S, RPM Film Studios, South Africa, 1970.</ref> Harimo n'indirimbo "Shangani Patrol" ya Nick Taylor (recording 1966).

Ku buyobozi bwa Major Wilson, irondo rikurikirana umwami Ndebele Lobengula wahunze hakurya y'uruzi rwa Shangani. Bagabanijwe ku mbaraga nyamukuru, batewe igico na Ndebele impi kandi, usibye abagabo bake boherejwe nk'imbaraga, bose baricwa. Ubwo ni bwo butwari bw'irondo rya Shangani ku buryo Ndebele watsinze yagize ati: "Bari abagabo ariko na ba se bari abagabo mbere yabo." Ukurikije uko umuntu abibona, ibyabaye byari rimwe mu makosa akomeye no kwibeshya kwa gisirikare muri iki gihe cy'amateka, cyangwa igihagararo cyanyuma cyintwari cya bake. Ibyabaye byari bifite akamaro gakomeye mubwongereza, Afrika yepfo, na Rodeziya bihwanye na ' Custer's Last stand '. Ngiyo inkuru yabo, yavuzwe muri firime ya 1970 yafatiwe ahitwa Matabeleland, Rhodesia (ubu ni muri [[Zimbabwe]]).
